No. —, Original.

Ex parte: In the Matter of Oregon Eilers Music House, Petitioner. Submitted October 4, 1921. Decided October 24, 1921. Mr. Will R. King, Mr. Thomas Mannix and Mr. C. A. A. McGee for petitioner. Mr. Levi Cooke and Mr. William C. Bristol for respondent.

Motion for leave to file petition for a writ of prohibition herein dénied.
